    <ul>
        <li><a href="/docs/lifecycle">Lifecycle</a> — onStart, onShutdown, cleanup hooks</li>
        <li><a href="/docs/actions#url">Actions → URL</a> — why <code>@post()</code> is required</li>
        <li><a href="/docs/api">API Reference</a> — Config class options (<code>withBasePath</code>, <code>withBrotli</code>, <code>withCertificate</code>, <code>withH2c</code>, <code>withTrustedOrigins</code>, <code>withSecureCookie</code>)</li>
    </ul>
</article>

{% endblock %}
